Discovers which categories use a given property and renders reverse relationship rows.

Called via format=template from Category/render-reverse's #ask query.
For each source category found, renders a table row showing pages that
reference the current page through this property. Pure wikitext table syntax.

Parameter 1: property page name (e.g. Property:Has department)

Row label format: "SourceCategory (relationship)" where relationship is the
property's Inverse property label, falling back to Display label, then property name.

Uses #arraymap with \n delimiter — empty results (count=0) are skipped.
Uses format=plainlist (not format=list) to avoid invisible SMW formatting spans.
Uses #ifexpr instead of #if because #if treats "0" as truthy.
</noinclude>
